### Grey Wallet API - Terms of Service Tests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### TERMS OF SERVICE TESTS
### ========================================

### 1. Get Latest Terms of Service
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/terms
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. Get Terms of Service by Version 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/terms/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 3. Get Terms of Service by Invalid Version (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/terms/999
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 4. Get Terms of Service by Invalid Version String (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/terms/invalid
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 5. Get Terms of Service by Negative Version (should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/terms/-1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
